We had a good meal here-   Habas a la catalana- Excellent -   Very good local dish. not very flashy but very good depth of flavor.  Nice unique bean dishChistorra - Very good sausageGambas Ajillo-  NOT Good these were very mushy shrimpTorrada Lomo Iberico - GoodPan Tostado con tomat - GoodOverall it was a very nice lunch.   The other dish that was different here was the batata bravas -  Our friends ordered this and they a little disappointed compared to other places they had this.
